title: Bump ejs from 1.0.0 to 2.5.5

labels.name: dependencies
labels.description: Pull requests that update a dependency file

body:
Bumps [ejs](https://github.com/mde/ejs) from 1.0.0 to 2.5.5.
Release notes *Sourced from [ejs's releases](https://github.com/mde/ejs/releases).* > ## v2.5.5 > - Allow 'filename' for opts-in-data, but sanitize when rendered ([@​mde](https://github.com/mde)) > > ## v2.5.4 > - Blackist more options from opts-in-data ([@​mde](https://github.com/mde)) > - Allow trailing comments in output modes ([@​mde](https://github.com/mde)) > - Added 'name' attribute for easy identification ([@​designfrontier](https://github.com/designfrontier)) > > ## v2.5.3 > - Blackist 'root' option from opts-in-data ([@​mde](https://github.com/mde)) > > ## v2.5.2 > - Added link to EJS Playground ([@​RyanZim](https://github.com/RyanZim)) > - Revert express auto 'root' option ([@​RyanZim](https://github.com/RyanZim)) > > ## v2.5.1 > - Output literal `%>` with `%%>` (Roy Miloh) > - Allow setting project root for includes ([@​cnwhy](https://github.com/cnwhy)) > - UMD support for the browser ([@​RyanZim](https://github.com/RyanZim)) > - Exported `escapeXML` method to allow manual escaping of output > - Tests for strict mode ([@​RyanZim](https://github.com/RyanZim), [@​mde](https://github.com/mde)) > - Added ESLint for project source code ([@​mde](https://github.com/mde)) > - Whitespace slurp in preprocessor include ([@​mmis1000](https://github.com/mmis1000)) > - Improved line-number handling in errors ([@​Spikef](https://github.com/Spikef)) > - Various doc improvements ([@​RyanZim](https://github.com/RyanZim), Ionică Bizău) > > ## v2.4.2 > - Added LICENSE file to release package > - Various documentation improvements ([@​RyanZim](https://github.com/RyanZim)) > - Better line-numbers in errors ([@​dgofman](https://github.com/dgofman)) > > ## v2.4.1 > - Strict-mode support ([@​mde](https://github.com/mde)) > - Express 4 support ([@​mde](https://github.com/mde)) > - Configurable localsName option ([@​mde](https://github.com/mde)) > > ## v2.3.4 > - Whitespace slurp tag syntax -- `<%_ _%>` ([@​andidev](https://github.com/andidev)) > > ## v2.3.3 > No release notes provided. > > ## v2.3.2 > No release notes provided. > > ## v2.3.1 > No release notes provided. > > ## v2.2.4 > - Ability to customize name of the locals object with `ejs.localsName` ([@​mde](https://github.com/mde)) > ... (truncated)
Changelog *Sourced from [ejs's changelog](https://github.com/mde/ejs/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md).* > ## v2.5.5: 2016-12-06 > > * Allow 'filename' for opts-in-data, but sanitize when rendered ([@​mde](https://github.com/mde)) > > ## v2.5.4: 2016-12-05 > > * Blackist more options from opts-in-data ([@​mde](https://github.com/mde)) > * Allow trailing comments in output modes ([@​mde](https://github.com/mde)) > + Added 'name' attribute for easy identification ([@​designfrontier](https://github.com/designfrontier)) > > ## v2.5.3: 2016-11-28 > > * Blackist 'root' option from opts-in-data ([@​mde](https://github.com/mde)) > > ## v2.5.2: 2016-07-25 > > + Added link to EJS Playground ([@​RyanZim](https://github.com/RyanZim)) > - Revert express auto 'root' option ([@​RyanZim](https://github.com/RyanZim)) > > ## v2.5.1: 2016-07-25 > > + Output literal `%>` with `%%>` (Roy Miloh) > + Allow setting project root for includes ([@​cnwhy](https://github.com/cnwhy)) > + UMD support for the browser ([@​RyanZim](https://github.com/RyanZim)) > + Exported `escapeXML` method to allow manual escaping of output ([@​mde](https://github.com/mde)) > + Tests for strict mode ([@​RyanZim](https://github.com/RyanZim), [@​mde](https://github.com/mde)) > + Added ESLint for project source code ([@​mde](https://github.com/mde)) > * Whitespace slurp in preprocessor include ([@​mmis1000](https://github.com/mmis1000)) > * Improved line-number handling in errors ([@​Spikef](https://github.com/Spikef)) > * Various doc improvements ([@​RyanZim](https://github.com/RyanZim), Ionică Bizău) > > ## v2.4.2: 2016-05-24 > > + Added LICENSE file to release package > * Various documentation improvements ([@​RyanZim](https://github.com/RyanZim)) > * Better line-numbers in errors ([@​dgofman](https://github.com/dgofman)) > > ## v2.4.1: 2016-01-23 > > + Strict-mode support ([@​mde](https://github.com/mde)) > + Express 4 support ([@​mde](https://github.com/mde)) > + Configurable localsName option ([@​mde](https://github.com/mde)) > > ## v2.3.4: 2015-09-04 > > + Whitespace slurp tag syntax -- `<%_ _%>` ([@​andidev](https://github.com/andidev)) > > ## v2.3.3: 2015-07-11 > > * Fixed false positives for old `include` preprocessor directive ([@​mde](https://github.com/mde)) > ...
